longBusinessSummary: Flameret, Inc., a development stage company, focuses on manufacturing and distributing fire barrier product named Flameret. The Flameret is a flame retardant liquid applied to textiles for producing mattresses, to resist ignition from smoldering cigarettes, and to impede ignition from open-flame heat sources. It offers products comprising Flameret, a textile FR treatment; Ultra Flamex, a fire extinguishing product; and Impex. The company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Venice, Florida.
